{"id":643749,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/【颂歌新赛季】母亲节篇-习近平与母亲的6个瞬间/","date":"2020-05-11T06:24:11Z","modified":"2020-05-11T06:24:11Z","title":"【颂歌新赛季】母亲节篇 习近平与母亲的6个瞬间","content":"<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>中国数字空间｜</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%B4%87%E6%8B%9C\"><strong>颂歌新赛季</strong></a></p></blockquote>\n<p>2020年5月10日母亲节，官方媒体“中央广播电视总台央视网”发起对习近平和母亲之间的亲子关系宣传，赞扬其母亲的“言传身教”，也称颂习近平的“尽孝”。</p>\n<p>————————</p>\n<p><strong>以下为原文：</strong></p>\n<p>“慈母手中线，游子身上衣。临行密密缝，意恐迟迟归。谁言寸草心，报得三春晖。”在2015年春节团拜会上，习近平总书记深情吟诵了唐代诗人孟郊的《游子吟》。</p>\n<p>为人父母天下至善，为人子女天下大孝。</p>\n<p>作为母亲，孩子平安喜乐，便是最大的欣慰。而母亲齐心对习近平的期望中，更多了一份对国家和人民的责任与担当。母亲的言传身教让习近平受用一生。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643754\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2316c2b05a747bec5af7e26f200b47c0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2316c2b05a747bec5af7e26f200b47c0.jpg 750w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2316c2b05a747bec5af7e26f200b47c0-200x300.jpg 200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2316c2b05a747bec5af7e26f200b47c0-683x1024.jpg 683w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_643757\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-643757\" class=\"wp-image-643757\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081374570.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081374570.jpg 750w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081374570-200x300.jpg 200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081374570-683x1024.jpg 683w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-643757\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">图片来源：《习近平的七年知青岁月》</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_643756\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-643756\" class=\"wp-image-643756\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081081546.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081081546.jpg 750w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081081546-200x300.jpg 200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081081546-683x1024.jpg 683w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-643756\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">图片来源：《习仲勋画传》</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643755\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100080759989.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100080759989.jpg 750w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100080759989-200x300.jpg 200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100080759989-683x1024.jpg 683w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-643758 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081657158.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081657158.jpg 750w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081657158-200x300.jpg 200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081657158-683x1024.jpg 683w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643759\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081912480.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081912480.jpg 750w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081912480-200x300.jpg 200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/2020051100081912480-683x1024.jpg 683w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n","author":1069,"categories":[18271,38912,38918],"tags":[27046,13222,32609,13335,9540,26170,21038,10307]}